title: Full Day Pilgrims
description: Surround yourself with the ancient Incan history on a sightseeing tour to three of Lima's archaeological sights. Complimentary transportation takes you from the city center to the settlements of Huallamarca, Pucllana, and Pachacamac. At each location, listen as your guide goes beyond the guidebook and paints a vivid picture of life as it was when these sites were bustling cities. Lunch and snacks are included.

Awesome day, awesome guide!

Aug 2024 • Couples
We had such a great time on the tour with Juan as our guide! He was super knowledgeable about the history of the site and shared it in a really interesting way that kept us hooked. Juan’s storytelling made the ancient cultures feel so real. The tour was well-planned, with plenty of chances to explore and ask all the questions we had. We left with a whole new appreciation for Peru’s history. Big thanks to Juan for making the day so fun and memorable!
